From 4d0a6cafb57a64f0d5c1be7eb07f45821dc7fa12 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Bjorn Nordblom <bjorn.nordblom@riverty.com>
Date: Wed, 1 Apr 2026 11:31:50 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] feat: preserve comments and blank lines in script generator

- Add PreserveComments option to SqlScriptGeneratorOptions
- Walk raw token stream between fragments to emit comments in-place
- Preserve structural blank lines between statements and after GO
- Fix GO batch separator spacing
- Add comprehensive regression tests

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
